branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The MGT integrates a high precision bearing manual turntable with a MGP, standard guided actuator. The turntable has an embedded positioning mechanism each at 90&#xb0; and 180&#xb0; of rotation detected by an auto-switch sensor. The (L) high precision ball bushing allows for smooth operation that ensures stable travel resistance, suitable for pushing and lifting applications. The (M) carbon steel alloy slide bearing provides lateral stability protecting it from side load impacts, suitable for stopping applications.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bore sizes: 63, 80, 100 mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stroke lengths: 25, 50, 75, 100, 125, 150, 175, 200 mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

